{
  "texts": [
    "The experiments are carried out on a Windows 11 machine, with an Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-1195 G7 @ 2.90GHz processor, single core (of 4-total) was used for all experimentation presented.",
    "The GiBy-core detector (Section 3) and extended algorithm (Section 4) are used.",
    "The SWaT normal dataset is used for training and attack dataset is for testing.",
    "TABLE 4 shows the attacks that are detected by GiBy.",
    "Attacks 5, 9, 12, 15 and 18 in TABLE 4 had no physical impact on the system."
